that is my YAML. Title, author, I switched the date out, not in the thing you can see,

00:14:21.400 --> 00:14:25.039
the date's actually here, but in the final version, I switched the date out from my Twitter

00:14:25.039 --> 00:14:29.919
handle, changed the font size, pretty much that's all I had to do to the YAML, and away

00:14:29.919 --> 00:14:33.119
you go, writing R Markdown. Super good.

00:14:33.119 --> 00:14:37.599
My CV, which had been maintained for years, I thought we could do this in R Markdown too,

